# Summary
This documentation details the Amplitude Data integration with Planhat, allowing real-time streaming of user activity events to Planhat for customer success management. The integration matches Amplitude user_ids to Planhat externalIds, requires tenant token authentication, and enables various use cases including health scoring, opportunity creation, and workflow automation based on product usage data.

